{"tid":668534,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲會有人玩LOL?","createTime":"2018-05-17T16:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T02:07:16.000Z","uid":70429,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc88e7981cfee5c16d12bee259d5b2fda52b9c9","tid":668534,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"以前一日幾鋪,<br />\n<br />\n如今一個禮拜一鋪,<br />\n<br />\n打完即刻覺得好累.<br />\n<br />\n而且班台狗又要鐘意嘴炮,<br />\n<br />\n無論對面隊定自己隊,<br />\n<br />\n順風時比人圍死就屌對面:''3個打1個?爭氣點好嗎?''<br />\n<br />\n逆風時就屌自己隊:''3個都殺不掉1個?爭氣點好嗎?<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就:''玩個遊戲都那麼爛?你是喜戇兒嗎?''<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地打依d句子,我會覺得好唔好意思,好尷尬...打場機姐洗唔洗R存在感R虛榮感.<br />\n<br />\n隻game個娛樂性越來越低,相比之下好容易令人暴怒,發脾氣,暴戾.<br />\n<br />\n一陣我驚有人屌我脾氣差EQ低先會咁,<br />\n<br />\n講定先,  平時成隻老綿羊咁,冇脾氣,冇火氣,而且做服務業,EQ比客人訓練到好堅韌."},{"pid":"6568f7e957cee3ff2385f9745ac6b091b9379abb","tid":668534,"uid":157138,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"打個機姐 入場mute晒佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ea1c80b0145ada78649ec732e8dae29f26ad87","tid":668534,"uid":52299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"互屌先係呢隻game 既精髓"},{"pid":"baebad34a47362f8813e8277e745668a57d7ede8","tid":668534,"uid":78856,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T20:49:20.000Z","msg":"台狗班小學雞根本弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢地講野都晒撚氣"},{"pid":"03b89551bff669de1e8b090986d4a39b0089a643","tid":668534,"uid":148541,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T21:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7b3e3735ed7b62c6dd09de071ffec30e59a0f6c","tid":668534,"uid":162783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"baebad34a47362f8813e8277e745668a57d7ede8","tid":668534,"uid":78856,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T20:49:20.000Z","msg"